      "Code": "//Function to get params\ndef GetParams(crv,s)\n{\nlen = Curve.Length(crv)/s;\ncei = Math.Ceiling(len);\nspc = 1/cei;\ncel = Curve.Length(crv)/cei;\nseq = spc/2..1-spc/2..#cei;\nreturn [seq,cel];\n};\n\np1 = GetParams(crv[0],s);\np2 = GetParams(crv[1],s);\n\n//Parameters\np1[0];\np2[0];\n\n//Final Cell size\np1[1];\np2[1];"
